  "text": "Dai proposed a modified CFAR algorithm [CITATION_1] ) that improves the detection accuracy by setting the size of the protection window according to the sizes of objects. Schwegmann proposed a ship detection algorithm based on deep learning [CITATION_2] ) that improves the detection accuracy largely by training on samples. Kang proposed an R-CNN ship detection algorithm based on the CFAR algorithm ) that improves ship detection performance by combining pixel and depth features.",
